## Python Tools

In `P:/Projects2/sg-general-agents/projects/prospector/data-sources/tools/`:
- `extract_pdf.py` — PDF text extraction with page ranges and keyword search
- `filter_acara.py` — XLSX filtering with school name matching and aggregation (Australia only)
- `acara_trends.py` — Historical enrolment trend extraction (Australia only)
- `validate_schema.py` — Schema validation for pipeline output files

Agents should call these via Bash to avoid loading large files into context.

