### Phase 6: Schema Validation

Run schema validation before deploying. This step MUST pass before the deploy step.

Use the `pipeline-schema-validator` agent with:
- `ORG_ID`: `{{ORG_ID}}`
- `ORG_DIR`: `P:/Projects2/sg-general-agents/projects/prospector/data-sources/{{ORG_ID}}`

Fix any failures before continuing.

## Final Step: Deploy to Site

Use the merge tool for keyed JSON files, and copy for standalone files.

Tool: `python P:/Projects2/sg-general-agents/projects/prospector/data-sources/tools/merge_json_key.py <target> <key> <source>`

```bash
TOOLS="P:/Projects2/sg-general-agents/projects/prospector/data-sources/tools"
SITE="P:/Projects2/sg-general-agents/projects/prospector/site/public/data"
ORG="P:/Projects2/sg-general-agents/projects/prospector/data-sources/{{ORG_ID}}"

# Keyed merges (insert/replace the "{{ORG_ID}}" key in target files)
python $TOOLS/merge_json_key.py $SITE/companies/pain-points-v3.json {{ORG_ID}} $ORG/analysis/pain-points.json
python $TOOLS/merge_json_key.py $SITE/companies/opportunities.json {{ORG_ID}} $ORG/analysis/opportunities.json
python $TOOLS/merge_json_key.py $SITE/companies/market-solutions.json {{ORG_ID}} $ORG/assembled/market-solutions.json
python $TOOLS/merge_json_key.py $SITE/companies/indicators.json {{ORG_ID}} $ORG/assembled/signals.json
python $TOOLS/merge_json_key.py $SITE/companies/lookalikes.json {{ORG_ID}} $ORG/assembled/lookalikes.json
python $TOOLS/merge_json_key.py $SITE/companies/competitive-landscape.json {{ORG_ID}} $ORG/assembled/competitors.json

# Direct copies (standalone files per org)
cp $ORG/assembled/profile.json $SITE/profiles/{{ORG_ID}}.json
cp $ORG/assembled/scorecard.json $SITE/profiles/{{ORG_ID}}-scorecard.json
```

## Core Principle

**Extract, don't generate.** Every fact cites a document. Every inference states the chain. Every unknown is flagged. If you can't find something, write it as a gap — never fabricate.

